    <item>
      <title>Message Center | Update v7.0.4</title>
      <pubDate>Saturday, 6 Nov 2021</pubDate>
      <description>
	&lt;h1&gt;NEW FEATURES&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;ul class=&quot;bb_ul&quot;&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; Message Center: The Message Center will contain messages pertaining Phasmophobia, P.E.T., and teritary general Phasmophobia-related news.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; General News: Supplementary, non-changelog type information pertaining to Phasmophobia and P.E.T. Find information about official community events, or get notified about any new future plans for P.E.T.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; P.E.T. Change-log: Stay up-to-date with the changes to P.E.T. by reading the official developer change-logs!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; Phasmophobia Change-log: Stay up-to-date with the changes to Phasmophobia by reading the official developer change-logs!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; Ability to disable Mobile Data usage for the Message Center.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;h1&gt;FIXES&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;ul class=&quot;bb_ul&quot;&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; The Title Screen had an issue where the animations would cause app crashes. There should no longer be crashes from this.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt; User-selected language should now be default on the Title Screen.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
      </description>
